<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시글 수정 페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("common/header.ejs"); %>
    <div id="container">
        <%- include("common/banner.ejs"); %>
        <div class="center">
            <h3>수정하기</h3>
            <div class="formpre">
                <p>지엔테크 제품에 대한 <span>궁금한 사항이나 관련 자료</span>가 필요하신 분들은 문의 글을 남겨주세요.<br>담당자 확인 후 전화나 메일로 답변드리겠습니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="brd_upt">
                <form id="myform" action="/update" method="post">
                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%- data.brdid %>">
                    <div class="inputBox">
                        <label for="auther">작성자</label>
                        <input id="auther" type="text" name="auther" value="<%- data.brdauther %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="inputBox">
                        <label for="title">제목</label>
                        <input id="title" type="text" name="title" value="<%- data.brdtitle %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="txtBox">
                        <label for="context">문의사항</label>
                        <textarea id="context" name="context"><%- data.brdcontext %></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sub_Btn">
                    <button type="submit">수정</button>
                    <a href="/list">취소</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("common/footer.ejs"); %>
</body>
</html>